  "original_title": "\u0daf\u0dd9\u0dc0\u0dd0\u0db1\u0dd2 \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dca\u200d\u0dba\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dcf\u0dbb \u0db8\u0ddc\u0da9\u0dd4\u0dba\u0dbd\u0dba \u0d85\u0db7\u0dca\u200d\u0dba\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dc1\u0d9c\u0dad \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd3\u0db8\u0da7 \u0dc3\u0dd0\u0dbb\u0dc3\u0dda",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The second laboratory module is about to be launched",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "China's second laboratory module, Mengtian, prepares for launch, the final component of China's space station.",
        "To this end, a Long March-5B Y4 carrier rocket has been transported to the Wenchang Spacecraft Launch Site in southern China's Hainan Province, where it is ready for assembly and testing, the China Manned Space Agency (CMS) announced.",
        "The lab module has been assembled and is undergoing tests after being moved to the launch site in early August."
      ],
